kdna-react provides React components and hooks for building
KDNA-integrated web applications. Components handle file selection,
load-plan state, password entry, license activation, asset inspection,
and asset creation.

This package builds on @aikdna/kdna-web-client for browser-safe
operations. Decryption and license verification are always delegated
to a server running @aikdna/kdna-web-server.

